4px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; line-height: 60px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\">微循环畅通百病不生--微循环障碍是百病之源</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">微循环是血液流经细小的微动脉，经过毛细血管，流向微静脉的循环。它的主要功能是向组织细胞运送氧气和养料，带走细胞生产的二氧化碳和其他代谢产物。当微循环衰退时，人体的老化也就开始了，所以许多专家称微循环为人体的第二心脏。</span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">许多专家把毛细血管形态上的改变，以及血流形态上的改变所引起的功能性能改变称之为微循环障碍。如果微循环的血管变形，血管堵塞不通，由此引起的细胞缺血，器官组织及缺氧性细胞坏死，从而产生病变。</span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">微循环障碍会引起下列后果：<span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #9933cc;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;\">1、血容量相对或绝对不组；2、代谢紊乱，使组织细胞缺血，酸中毒而产生一系列严重的后果；3、内脏受累；4、严重的可发生弥漫性血管内凝血。</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 楷体_gb2312; color: #9933cc; font-size: 18pt;\">常见病：高血压、冠心病、脑血栓、糖尿病、颈椎病、腰腿病、风湿、类风湿性关节炎、脉管炎、肩周炎、神经衰弱、偏头痛、肿瘤、心率不高等。</span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 18pt;\">神奇的纳米材料</span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #000099; font-size: 9pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"color: #000099; font-size: 13.5pt;\">纳米&rdquo;是物理学上的长度计量单位，<span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000099;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: medium;\">1</span>纳米等于<span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: medium;\">10</span>亿分之一米，直径相当于一根头发丝的</span></span></span><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 13.5pt;\">五万分之一。科学实验证明，当常规材料用科学手段，使组成物质的微晶结构达到纳米级时，其物质就会发生奇特的物理和化学突变，具有极高的活性，潜在极大的原始能量。它们的物理、化学、生物特性会发生许多意想不到的奇特变化</span><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 9pt;\">，</span><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 13.5pt;\">这便是我们常说的<span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #008000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: medium;\">\"</span>从量变到质变</span></span></span><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 9pt;\">\"</span><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 9pt;\">。</span><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 13.5pt;\">比如原来是导体的铜等金属，在尺寸减小到几纳米时就不导电了</span><span style=\"color: green; font-size: 9pt;\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; color: #330099; font-size: 18pt;\">材质：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: fuchsia; font-size: 12pt;\">从珍稀天然矿石（含有<span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #ff00ff;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体;\">20多种微量元素）中提取，加工到纳米级别，与丙纶混溶喷丝而成。</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 60px; background-color: white;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><span class=\"active0\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_gb2312; color: fuchsia; font-size: 18pt;\">原理<span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #ff00ff; font-size: large;\">:</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #674ea7; font-size: 13.5pt;\">发射生物波与人体产生共振，从而达到排除人体毒素，打通微循环，调整新陈代谢的功能。。</span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 