 clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;微循环畅通百病不生--微循环障碍是百病之源</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: large;\"></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;微循环是血液流经细小的微动脉，经过毛细血管，流向微静脉的循环。它的主要功能是向组织细胞运送氧气和养料，带走细胞生产的二氧化碳和其他代谢产物。当微循环衰退时，人体的老化也就开始了，所以许多专家称微循环为人体的第二心脏。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: large;\"></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;许多专家把毛细血管形态上的改变，以及血流形态上的改变所引起的功能性能改变称之为微循环障碍。如果微循环的血管变形，血管堵塞不通，由此引起的细胞缺血，器官组织及缺氧性细胞坏死，从而产生病变。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: large;\"></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;微循环障碍会引起下列后果：1、血容量相对或绝对不组；2、代谢紊乱，使组织细胞缺血，酸中毒而产生一系列严重的后果；3、内脏受累；4、严重的可发生弥漫性血管内凝血。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: large;\"></span></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; color: #000000; font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-family: kaiti_gb2312;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;常见病：高血压、冠心病、脑血栓、糖尿病、颈椎病、腰腿病、风湿、类风湿性关节炎、脉管炎、肩周炎、神经衰弱、偏头痛、肿瘤、心率不高等。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, clean, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-break: break-all; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-heig