ly: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; orphans: 2; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px;\">生理年轻化。血压等指标平稳，心脏功能平稳，女性更年期症状消失，老年性耳鸣耳聋眼花等症状减轻等。</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 21px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; orphans: 2; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px;\">重获青春！延缓衰老！就是&ldquo;端利美&rdquo;！</div>','1721','美食特产	营养品	药食同源食品','纳豆','0','','','1','0',null,'1402470880','1402552971','254','data/files/store_67/goods_165/small_201406112312458787.jpg','1','1705','1716','1721','0','1680.00','0','');
