2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">【生产日期】：见外包装盒</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">【保质</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">期】：</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\';\">24</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">个月</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br /></span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 32px; color: #8f0197;\">产品成分：</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 32px; color: #8f0197;\"><br /></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【纳豆激酶】</span>是直接分解血栓的纤维蛋白酶。具有强大的溶栓作用，而且安全、无副作用。食用纳豆后，血液中形成血栓的物质会慢慢减少，<span style=\"background-color: #013add;\"><span style=\"color: #013add;\"><span style=\"color: #0021b0; background-color: #ffffff;\">溶解血栓</span></span></span>的物质会越来越多，达到动态平衡。</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【大豆多肽】</span>也称大豆蛋白肽，具有高营养、易吸收、降血压、降胆固醇、促进脂质代谢、促进微生物生长、低抗原、调节血糖、提高耐力、促进矿物质吸收等多种生理功能。</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【卵磷脂】</span>被誉为与</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\';\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">蛋白质、维生素</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\';\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">并列的第三营养素，能分解沉积于动脉壁上的斑块，促进血管的弹性及增进血液循环。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【大豆异黄酮】</span>有降低血脂、防止动脉硬化、<span style=\"color: #013add;\">抗衰老</span>作用。</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体; background-color: #feed9b;\">【维生素</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\'; background-color: #feed9b;\">K2(Vitamin K2)</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">】</span>可预防肝硬化进展为肝癌，具有利尿、强化肝脏的解毒功能，并能降低血压。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【葛根】</span>对高血压、高血脂、高血糖和心脑血管疾病有很好作用。葛根素能降低血糖，能明显降低血清胆固醇。同时对**，尤其是冠心病、骨质疏松症、妇女更年期综合症和老年性痴呆等有预防作用！</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; margin-top: 1.12em; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><strong>【厚德物质】王厚德独秘配方，能</strong><strong>促使<span style=\"color: #013add;\">端粒酶</span>活性增强</strong><strong>，<span style=\"color: #013add;\">延缓衰老</span>，恢复青春状态之作用。</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt; font-size: 14px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 32px; color: #8f0197;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 32px; font-family: 宋体; color: #8f0197;\">纳豆胶囊</span><span style=\"font-size: 32px; font-family: 宋体; color: #8f0197;\">溶栓四步曲</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 32px; font-family: 宋体; color: #8f0197;\"><br /></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【第一阶段：溶质除杂活血液】：</span>纳豆胶囊中的<span style=\"font-size: 32px; color: #f10b00;\">纳豆激酶</span>进入人体血管后，开始溶解血管中的杂质，使血液逐步活起来。此时，患者胸闷心慌、头晕眼花、失眠、手脚发麻僵硬等症状逐渐消失，血压、血脂开始降低。</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【第二阶段：溶栓通血降三高】：</span>纳豆胶囊服用一段时期后，吸收的纳豆激酶增多，使血栓逐渐溶解，血液开始循环通畅，避免了二次中风的危险</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\';\">;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">血压、血脂接近正常值、并且稳定</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\';\">;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">重病患者麻木的肢体，开始稍有知觉。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【第三阶段：扩管供血滋神经】：</span>纳豆胶囊中的纳豆激酶增强了血管弹性，使管腔逐渐增大，血液供应更加充分</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\';\">;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">脑部神经得到了有效滋润，侧肢循环更加密集发达</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: \'times new roman\';\">;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">重病患者语言功能开始恢复，原来口齿不清的人，说话能成句了，眼睛有神，感觉肢体有力。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; orphans: 2; widows: 2; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"background-color: #feed9b;\">【第四阶段：清血排脂回