 5; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes;\">\r\n<td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 193.5pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 22.5pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt;\" width=\"258\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-left: 18pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">测试护垫</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 211.5pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 22.5pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid windowtext .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid windowtext .5pt;\" width=\"282\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 36pt; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">包</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"> X 2</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">片</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>丝然卫生巾采用新一代环保材料&mdash;&mdash;无纺布，柔韧、透气、环保，更呵护肌肤；表层根据人体曲线专设防侧漏边、漏斗形导流孔、导流槽，内含吸水因子，充分吸收潮涌，超强锁水，周全防护，时刻保持干爽感觉。更有创新芯片&mdash;&mdash;集静态负离子、磁性、远红外、银离子、锗元素五合一，由纯植物纤维制成，具有杀菌、除异味、改善微循环、消炎等功效，给您更多健康！</p>\r\n<p><strong>&middot;无纺布</strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>无纺布是由定向的或随机的纤维构成，是新一代环保材料，具有透气防水、柔韧、无毒无味、无刺激性等特点。</p>\r\n<p><strong>&middot;</strong><strong>芯片</strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>集静态负离子、磁性、红外线、银离子、锗元素五合一，由纯植物纤维制成，给你更多健康！</p>\r\n<p><strong>&middot;</strong><strong>表层</strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>拥有防测漏边、漏斗形导流孔、导流槽。女性生理周期脆弱的生理环境更适合选用棉质表面，更加柔软、舒适、呵护肌肤令肌肤倍感舒适。</p>\r\n<p><strong>&middot;</strong><strong>吸水因子</strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>采用创新吸收体&mdash;&mdash;原木木浆，充分吸收潮涌，超强锁水，能提供更周全防护和超干爽感觉。原木木浆天然环保，营造更加舒适安全的生理环境。</p>\r\n<p><strong>&middot;</strong><strong>无尘纸、无尘棉</strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>无尘纸具有独特的物理性能，表现为高弹力，柔软、手感、垂感极佳，具有极高的吸水性和良好的保水性能，被广泛应用于卫生护理用品，特种医用用品、工业擦拭用品等领域。</p>\r\n<p><strong>&middot;</strong><strong>透气底膜</strong><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>底部采用凹点超透气呼吸膜，如呼吸般轻松透气，让你时刻保持放松状态！</p>','1386','日用百货	洗护清洁	卫生巾','','0','','','1','0',null,'1403841326','1404509570','422','data/files/store_392/goods_54/small_201406271954144285.jpg','1','1337','1385','1386','0','180.00','100','');
