line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">【围适用范】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适用于：风寒湿痹引起的颈肩腰腿痛等症、包括风湿、类风湿、关节炎、肩周炎、颈椎腰椎</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">病、骨质增生、骨刺、网球肘、腰椎间</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">盘突出、坐骨神经痛、腰肌劳损、跌打扭伤等。具有祛风除湿、消肿定痛、舒经活络、祛瘀止痛、活血驱风等功效。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">【产品性状】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">本品为咖啡色液体。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 24pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">【用法用量】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">外用喷于患处，每天</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\">1-2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">次，每次</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\">3-5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">喷或喷湿为宜。喷完后即用保护膜覆盖，</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\">1-2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">小时揭下即可。如同时配用电针灸，疗效更神奇！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">【规</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">格】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">每瓶60</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">ml</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">，每盒</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">瓶</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">【保质期】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">三年</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">【贮</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">藏</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">密封，避光、置阴凉干燥处存放</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 30pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">用药</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">分钟</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;\">，疼痛逐渐减轻改善，</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; font-size: 15pt;\">2&mdash;3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;\">天后；膝，肘，肩，颈等关节疼痛，僵硬，麻木等症明显减轻，可以轻微的走动，僵直的脖子可以轻轻转<span style=\"font-size: 15pt;\">动，晚上失眠现象消失。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 30pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">个月后</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;\">，骨刺，骨质增生，椎间盘突出部位被软化，逐渐消除，排除体外（用药前后</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; font-size: 15pt;\">X</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;\">光片可以明显的对比看到）走路，上下楼不再困难，早上下床时脚也敢踩地。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 30pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana; font-size: 15pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; font-size: 15pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">个月左右</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15pt;\">，骨关节变形基本停止，各种疼痛，僵硬，麻木，酸痛基本消失，在不怕变天，骨刺，骨质增生基本消除，得到康复。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; font-size: 14pt;\">【蜂蝎仿生疗法】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; color: red; font-size: 14pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">皮肤吃药</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: yellow; color: red; font-size: 14pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">国际首创</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; font-size: 14pt;\">【蜂蝎骨宝】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">通络透骨液主要成份为蜂毒、蝎毒、蚁酸、经典中药组方、微量元素等。其蜂蝎毒素是通过特殊有机态微量元素饲料喂养，经活体转化后采用弱毒化技术处理而成。通过添加目前国际最先进的透皮促进剂，可以促使</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">蜂蝎毒分子针</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">携带经典中药组方成份不仅能穿透皮肤、肌肉、骨膜层直达病灶给药，而且起到穴位针灸作用，并通络透骨参与血液循环。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">它的问世，彻底克服的传统疗法的种种弊端，属于国际首创，是世界先进医学技术和传统针灸学相结合的伟大成就。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; font-size: 14pt;\">【蜂蝎骨宝】<span style=\"background-color: yellow; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">开创骨病外治新时代</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">大自然的神奇造化蜂毒、蝎毒，用于治疗风湿骨病已经有</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">2300</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">多年的历史。大量的医学资料证实，在目前所有治疗风湿骨病的药物中，蜂毒、蝎毒的疗效是最为确切的！因为其中含有多种蜂毒肽、蝎毒肽、透明质酸酶、生物胺和其他活性物质，具有广泛的生物活性和药理作用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; font-size: 14pt;\">【蜂蝎骨宝】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">通络透骨液是上海大学、南京大学、安徽医学院、中国微量元素科学研究会等科研机构历经十一年开发研制的新型、高效治疗风湿类风湿的产品，其独创的蜂、蝎毒仿生疗法得到国际国内的广泛认证与肯定。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; font-size: 14pt;\">【蜂蝎骨宝】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">通络透骨液主要成份为蜂毒、蝎毒、蚁酸、经典中药组方、微量元素等。其蜂蝎毒素是通过特殊有机态微量元素饲料喂养，经活体转换后采用弱毒化处理而成。通过添加目前国际最先进的透皮促进剂，可以促使</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">蜂蝎毒分子针</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">携带经典中药组方成份不仅能穿透皮肤、肌肉、骨膜层直达病灶给药，而且起到穴位针灸作用，并通络透骨参与血液循环。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">它的问世，彻底克服了传统疗法的种种弊端，属国际首创，是世界先进医学技术和传统针灸学相结合的伟大成就，开创了骨病外治新时代。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; font-size: 14pt;\">【蜂蝎骨宝】</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">中含有</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">蜂蝎毒低链肽</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">，这种低链肽属于微分子物质，在高倍电子显微镜下呈针型，生物活性极强，对治疗风湿骨病有奇效。不仅能迅速穿透皮肤屏障，还能有效破除骨茧，拔出体内寒毒，使风湿骨病患者康复。这种</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">蜂蝎毒低链肽</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">医学上称之为</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">蜂蝎毒分子针</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">。蜂蝎仿生疗法</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">皮肤吃药</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">风湿骨病治疗骨关节病</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">蜂蝎毒分子针</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">直插骨关节</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">破茧拔毒骨病不不治疗，有瘫痪的危险！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">研究证实，中老年人、白领、特殊人群工作者（教师、野外工作者</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&hellip;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; font-size: 14pt;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">等是骨病的高发人群，疼痛起来，咬紧牙关还觉得难受，那个滋味，真不如死了算了特别是好多老人辛苦操劳了一辈子，落下了一身病根，本想再为儿女分忧，做做家务，但由于病痛折磨，身不由己，反成了累赘。自己心里愧疚不说，儿女也感到拖累。由于这多年顽疾久治不愈，很多老人都万念俱灰，甚至放弃了治疗。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">医学证实，无论何种骨病，长时间不治疗，都有瘫痪的危险！有权威医学单位统计：在我国局部地区，骨病的瘫痪率达到了</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">80%</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">以上！令人触目惊心！传统方法，不尽人意。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 24pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">目前，治疗风湿骨病的方法琳琅满目，口服药物、针灸推拿、手术</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&hellip;&hellip;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">，但不是久治不愈就是愈后复发，令众多患者苦不堪言。其原因不在于风湿骨病治不好，而在于治疗的路子没选对！口服服药物必须经肠胃吸收，通过血液，到达受损关节部位的毛细血管后才能发挥作用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 24pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">一方面，大量的口服药物会对肠胃粘膜造成不可修复的损伤，旧病未除，又添新伤！另一方面，由于病变部位早已形成坚硬的</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">骨茧</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">，药物有效成份被肠胃消化酶破坏后，很难再穿破骨茧，发挥作用。</span><span style=\"font-family: helvetica; font-size: 14pt;\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">针灸推拿，只是通过松弛肌肉，达到一时的疼痛减轻。手术治疗，只是消除骨茧，而对骨毒无能为力，等于治病不除根，为复发埋下隐患！综合比较</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">骨病外治最为合适。比较各种办法，使用骨病外治可使有效成份直达病灶、消除口服药物的刺激伤害，但传统贴剂都存在无法解决的技术难题：药物无法完全渗透皮肤这一人体天然屏障，有效成份难以进入皮肤、肌肉、穿透骨膜到达病灶部位，严重影响治疗效果！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 28pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">本品融合生物技术、经典组方，并依据现代元素医学理论，研发出高倍量浓缩醇制剂，是目前新型仿生细胞激活剂。采用特殊工艺，使有效活性成份得以最大化保全；不含激素类成份，提高免疫力，增加自身免疫修复功能；添加了目前国际最先进的透皮促进剂，使本品具有见效快、疗效高、稳定性佳等优良品质！</span></p>','2619','保健品	保健功效	缓解体力疲劳','天泽','0','','','0','0',null,'1404602200','1404680929','455','data/files/store_275/goods_125/small_201407071308458421.jpg','1','2595','2616','2619','0','0.00','80','');
