rif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><strong>【型号】：</strong><span style=\"line-height: 24px; background-color: #f6f6f6; text-indent: 5px; font-family: \'tahoma arial 宋体\'; white-space: nowrap;\">10.212.017</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">【包装】：卡纸</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 36px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">【产地】：德国本土代购，非国内专柜代理</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><br /></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">【宝贝描述】：</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">1.宽口奶瓶调奶和清洗方便。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">2.NUK宽口奶嘴扁圆形仿真造型，宝宝吸奶就像吸母乳一样亲切。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">3.自动进气孔能让宝宝吸奶时空气自动进入奶瓶中，保持一定压力，<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000;\">宝宝吸奶更轻松，奶嘴不会吸瘪。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000;\">4.宽口奶嘴是按照宝宝的舌、颚、齿龈和嘴唇的轮廓设计的，是一种</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000;\">天然的喂养方法，有助于宝宝口腔和牙齿的发育。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000;\">5.宝宝吸奶时奶嘴洞孔朝上，能让牛奶和唾液充分混合，有助于更好</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000;\">的消化。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000;\">6.NUK奶嘴接近母乳喂养，所以从母乳喂养转为人工喂养使用NUK奶嘴</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000;\">，宝宝能很快适应。</span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><img src=\"file:///c:/DOCUME~1/ADMINI~1/APPLIC~1/360se6/USERDA~1/Temp/T1RAI6~1.WEB\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\">请买家注意：</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline; color: #6600ff;\">最近有不少交流反映NUK的玻璃奶瓶底有貌似裂开的曲线状纹路</span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mceinline;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong></strong></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #6600ff;\">其实这是原厂里奶瓶的模具内的纹路，制造奶瓶时自然会在奶瓶上产生相同的纹路。</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: mceinline; color: #6600ff;\">每个NUK的玻璃奶瓶底上都有的，奶瓶质量是完全没有问题的。</span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2176','母婴用品	宝宝用品	奶瓶','德国原装NUK','2','颜色','尺码','1','0',null,'1405387100','1405387260','574','data/files/store_96/goods_2/small_201407151716423725.jpg','1','2108','2173','2176','0','99.00','1',',120ML,');
